113
00:09:27,161 --> 00:09:28,494
Right?

114
00:09:28,494 --> 00:09:33,744
How about you give it a try, Sou?

115
00:09:33,744 --> 00:09:36,894
No, I couldn't do it.

116
00:09:36,894 --> 00:09:38,311
Sure you can!

117
00:09:38,311 --> 00:09:40,619
Ow!

118
00:09:40,619 --> 00:09:43,086
My back.

119
00:09:43,086 --> 00:09:44,603
Not today.

120
00:09:44,603 --> 00:09:45,853
Oops.

121
00:09:45,853 --> 00:09:48,203
<i>[Vent to me!]</i>

122
00:09:48,203 --> 00:09:51,311
Come vent to me about everything.

123
00:09:52,490 --> 00:09:58,361
I'll suck it all up without leaving a single drop!

124
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:06,030
I mean... tell me about your problems!

125
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:08,936
Offered for free now.

126
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:13,711
I'd like to complain.

127
00:10:13,711 --> 00:10:16,728
Of course! Please.

128
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:23,286
Can I take your temperature first?

129
00:10:23,286 --> 00:10:24,786
Okay.

130
00:10:27,390 --> 00:10:31,228
35.8 Celsius. You're fine.

131
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:36,686
So, fire away.

132
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:43,178
