133
00:10:43,178 --> 00:10:45,378
Of course!

134
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,303
Okay then.

135
00:10:48,303 --> 00:10:50,945
You dumbo!

136
00:10:52,420 --> 00:10:54,437
