147
00:11:53,310 --> 00:11:55,529
Hello.

148
00:11:55,529 --> 00:11:57,521
Umm...

149
00:11:57,521 --> 00:11:59,930
I'll listen to your complaints.

150
00:11:59,930 --> 00:12:02,070
All right.

151
00:12:03,188 --> 00:12:05,304
Go ahead.

152
00:12:06,646 --> 00:12:09,813
