163
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:52,588
The woman from before...

164
00:12:54,996 --> 00:12:57,554
Why did I do that?

165
00:12:58,950 --> 00:13:01,221
I'm so stupid.

166
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:05,570
Stupid me! Why?

167
00:13:05,570 --> 00:13:07,670
Dummy! Idiot!

168
00:13:08,238 --> 00:13:12,413
What am I doing?

169
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:18,596
What is she doing?

170
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:25,004
Hey... sorry about earlier.

171
00:13:25,004 --> 00:13:29,590
I'll listen to your complaints if you want.

172
00:13:30,246 --> 00:13:32,129
Excuse me!

173
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:37,604
Are you okay?

174
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:41,064
Yeah.

175
00:13:41,064 --> 00:13:43,397
I'm fine.

176
00:13:44,439 --> 00:13:46,989
Ow...

177
00:14:08,610 --> 00:14:11,131
Bye!

178
00:14:11,131 --> 00:14:13,139
Wait a moment!

179
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:21,114
