191
00:15:12,272 --> 00:15:15,381
A yoga-loving vampire? Come on.

192
00:15:15,381 --> 00:15:17,422
Want to try? It feels good.

193
00:15:17,422 --> 00:15:19,030
Pass.

194
00:15:21,770 --> 00:15:25,706
