224
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:58,899
Excuse me?

225
00:17:58,899 --> 00:18:00,399
Yes?

226
00:18:09,149 --> 00:18:14,649
I'm so sorry I never came. To think you gave me your card...

227
00:18:14,649 --> 00:18:16,315
It's fine.

228
00:18:16,315 --> 00:18:18,915
So... you work here?

229
00:18:18,915 --> 00:18:21,590
Yes, I do.

230
00:18:26,315 --> 00:18:28,790
Kidney Stone...

231
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:33,207
"Monthly Kidney Stone" Editorial Department?

232
00:18:33,207 --> 00:18:38,377
Right, "Monthly Kidney Stone."

233
00:18:39,490 --> 00:18:41,399
It's that way.

234
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:44,515
Thanks.

235
00:18:47,450 --> 00:18:52,049
So, um, I have a meeting to get to.

236
00:19:01,832 --> 00:19:03,915
<i>You liar!</i>

237
00:19:03,915 --> 00:19:05,899
<i>I'm sorry...</i>

238
00:19:12,190 --> 00:19:15,243
This is not what you promised.

239
00:19:15,243 --> 00:19:19,151
You promised you'd persuade them.

240
00:19:19,151 --> 00:19:23,843
We won't accept your half-hearted excuses.

241
00:19:25,710 --> 00:19:27,166
I'm sorry...

242
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:32,638
