253
00:21:05,234 --> 00:21:07,384
Yeah?

254
00:21:07,384 --> 00:21:09,030
Yes.

255
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:10,800
Look there.

256
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:13,400
